data.value: 2.0 -complete layout redesign -disabling mods -contributors are now in settings -G E E S E -launcher will now automatically update (can be disabled in settings) -Beta Version button in settings (active for prerelease versions, these versions can have some bugs) -Mod Installation API (for mods not in one file) -Mod Configuration API (for mods with config file) -more links -warming when trying to install mods -button in settings for unlocking possibility of installing not safe mods (for your safety) -better descriptions
